00:51:36.720 --> 00:51:38.230
they go back and correct

00:51:38.240 --> 00:51:40.390
it, but some of them are so far off,

00:51:40.400 --> 00:51:42.549
it's going to take great correction.

00:51:58.400 --> 00:52:00.950
There's

00:52:00.960 --> 00:52:03.589
great correction coming. Many

00:52:03.599 --> 00:52:06.870
will see a

00:52:06.880 --> 00:52:10.950
humbling.

00:52:12.960 --> 00:52:15.430
I'm not picking on

00:52:15.440 --> 00:52:17.270
anybody.

00:52:17.280 --> 00:52:18.870
He just corrected me: 'You say

00:52:18.880 --> 00:52:24.390
what I

00:52:24.400 --> 00:52:34.870
say.'I

00:52:34.880 --> 00:52:39.430
repent, Lord. There's

00:52:39.440 --> 00:52:44.710
a shaking in the churches

00:52:44.720 --> 00:52:46.950
and you will see a great breaking,

00:52:46.960 --> 00:52:48.950
and they will come to their

00:52:48.960 --> 00:52:51.510
knees,

00:52:51.520 --> 00:53:01.349
for there is heresy.

00:53:14.480 --> 00:53:17.589
It's a stench before him each day.

00:53:26.240 --> 00:53:29.349
True repentance is to turn away.

00:53:32.960 --> 00:53:40.309
It's

00:53:46.400 --> 00:53:54.150
messy.

00:54:09.680 --> 00:54:11.349
You're going to see that even in the

00:54:11.359 --> 00:54:13.670
highest places in the land,

00:54:13.680 --> 00:54:16.230
even

00:54:16.230 --> 00:54:16.240
on

00:54:16.240 --> 00:54:22.950
TV.

00:54:22.960 --> 00:54:28.870
Tell

00:54:28.870 --> 00:54:28.880
them,

00:54:28.880 --> 00:54:30.390
'If you're a friend of the world, you're

00:54:30.400 --> 00:54:33.589
not a friend of

00:54:33.599 --> 00:54:36.069
me.'You've

00:54:36.079 --> 00:54:41.750
clung

00:54:41.760 --> 00:54:43.990
to the world and you've

00:54:44.000 --> 00:54:47.030
not clung to me. If you cling to the

00:54:47.040 --> 00:54:50.069
world, you don't cling to me.

00:54:50.079 --> 00:54:53.190
'Depart from me, I never knew

00:54:53.200 --> 00:54:56.630
you.'For

00:54:59.589 --> 00:54:59.599
there

00:55:02.069 --> 00:55:02.079
are

00:55:05.920 --> 00:55:07.829
many walking in

00:55:07.839 --> 00:55:16.069
heresy.

00:55:16.079 --> 00:55:17.829
Just because you tried to walk with the

00:55:17.839 --> 00:55:19.910
president, just because you walk with these

00:55:19.920 --> 00:55:26.790
people...

00:55:31.119 --> 00:55:33.109
it's messy.

00:55:33.119 --> 00:55:34.790
He says it

00:55:34.790 --> 00:55:34.800
is

00:55:34.800 --> 00:55:40.069
messy unto him. It's gross.

00:55:40.079 --> 00:55:43.030
Too much pride, and

00:55:43.040 --> 00:55:46.950
I resist the proud.

00:55:46.960 --> 00:55:49.990
Humble

00:55:50.000 --> 00:55:56.549
yourself unto me.

00:55:59.680 --> 00:56:01.990
In due time, I

00:56:02.000 --> 00:56:03.829
said I would exalt you. But there has

00:56:03.839 --> 00:56:07.829
not been time for many of them;

00:56:07.839 --> 00:56:11.349
they've exalted themselves.

00:56:20.720 --> 00:56:23.910
And he is angry about this. I hear his

00:56:23.920 --> 00:56:26.710
voice; he is trembling with

00:56:26.710 --> 00:56:26.720
the

00:56:26.720 --> 00:56:30.069
fear of God. 'The fear of the Lord

00:56:30.079 --> 00:56:33.190
is the beginning of wisdom.'The fear

00:56:33.200 --> 00:56:35.510
of the Lord, reverence,

00:56:35.520 --> 00:56:38.549
holiness, and purity must

00:56:38.549 --> 00:56:38.559
return to

00:56:38.559 --> 00:56:46.230
my church.

00:56:46.240 --> 00:56:47.750
You don't even know the

00:56:47.760 --> 00:56:49.109
difference between the church and the

00:56:49.119 --> 00:56:55.990
world today. He said,

00:56:56.000 --> 00:56:57.750
'Yet you say you're of me and you're

00:56:57.760 --> 00:56:59.510
my

00:57:01.349 --> 00:57:01.359
church.'This

00:57:12.559 --> 00:57:14.710
is in the purest of circles

00:57:14.720 --> 00:57:17.670
that you think you see, for there

00:57:17.670 --> 00:57:17.680
is

00:57:17.680 --> 00:57:20.630
great heresy and a great shaking coming

00:57:20.630 --> 00:57:20.640
to

00:57:20.640 --> 00:57:23.589
them. Even in the circles you

00:57:23.599 --> 00:57:25.109
think you

00:57:25.109 --> 00:57:25.119
know,

00:57:25.119 --> 00:57:28.390
remember this:

00:57:28.400 --> 00:57:31.510
I see them.

00:57:31.520 --> 00:57:34.309
Even in the ones that try to pretend

00:57:34.319 --> 00:57:37.270
they're the purest of me, their

00:57:37.280 --> 00:57:46.789
hearts are far from me.

00:57:46.799 --> 00:57:49.109
You don't

00:57:49.119 --> 00:57:54.870
have to yank on a horse's mouth

00:57:54.880 --> 00:57:56.950
hard to pull it off whenever it

00:57:56.950 --> 00:57:56.960
is

00:57:56.960 --> 00:57:59.430
in order.

00:57:59.440 --> 00:58:01.910
You don't have to yank on the bridle of

00:58:01.920 --> 00:58:04.230
a horse's mouth to make it have great

00:58:04.240 --> 00:58:06.630
correction.

00:58:06.640 --> 00:58:08.630
Great correction, if you yank it hard, is

00:58:08.640 --> 00:58:10.789
too much if the horse is in line with

00:58:10.799 --> 00:58:13.270
you; it just takes a little bit to guide

00:58:13.280 --> 00:58:18.870
it. But when a horse is rebellious,

00:58:18.880 --> 00:58:22.150
off track,

00:58:22.160 --> 00:58:24.710
and bucking around, it takes much

00:58:24.720 --> 00:58:27.190
strength. However, when you're on track with

00:58:27.200 --> 00:58:29.430
me, it doesn't take much correction; you

00:58:29.440 --> 00:58:32.470
barely have to pull it. He said, 'I see

00:58:32.480 --> 00:58:35.910
it. You barely have to pull it

00:58:35.920 --> 00:58:38.230
and you go right on

00:58:38.240 --> 00:58:41.670
track.'It

00:58:41.680 --> 00:58:44.230
doesn't take much to guide a broken

00:58:44.240 --> 00:58:46.390
horse.

00:58:46.400 --> 00:58:49.190
But when you are not broken,

00:58:49.200 --> 00:58:51.990
pliable,

00:58:51.990 --> 00:58:52.000
or

00:58:52.000 --> 00:58:57.990
ready,

00:58:58.000 --> 00:59:01.750
I see the horse and he guides it. You are

00:59:01.750 --> 00:59:01.760
like that

00:59:01.760 --> 00:59:04.230
horse; he's on it. He

00:59:04.240 --> 00:59:05.589
said, 'It barely takes a little

00:59:05.599 --> 00:59:09.270
tug, son, to stay on track.

00:59:09.280 --> 00:59:12.150
Move to the left; move to the right.

00:59:12.160 --> 00:59:14.390
Follow what I tell you

00:59:14.400 --> 00:59:16.950
to do.

00:59:16.960 --> 00:59:18.950
You're in sync with me and I'm in sync

00:59:18.960 --> 00:59:23.109
with you.'A horse that is broken is

00:59:23.119 --> 00:59:25.270
easily moved,

00:59:25.280 --> 00:59:28.870
but a horse that is rebellious

00:59:28.880 --> 00:59:42.309
takes much to break.

00:59:42.319 --> 00:59:44.630
He longs for you to have a

00:59:44.640 --> 00:59:51.030
relationship with him each day. He says,

00:59:51.040 --> 00:59:55.670
'You've grieved the heart of the Father.

01:00:00.720 --> 01:00:04.309
He's provided so much for you,

01:00:04.319 --> 01:00:06.150
but you've grieved the heart of the

01:00:06.150 --> 01:00:06.160
Father.'Oh

01:00:06.160 --> 01:00:14.150
Father,

01:00:14.160 --> 01:00:18.710
we repent.

01:00:18.720 --> 01:00:21.670
Forgive them, Father; forgive me,

01:00:21.680 --> 01:00:24.230
Lord. We come closer to you. You're

01:00:24.240 --> 01:00:27.510
such a good God.

01:00:27.520 --> 01:00:37.190
We repent, Lord. He

01:00:37.190 --> 01:00:37.200
says, 'You

01:00:37.200 --> 01:00:39.190
say you want the

01:00:39.200 --> 01:00:42.470
revival

01:00:42.470 --> 01:00:42.480
and

01:00:42.480 --> 01:00:48.870
the glory,

01:00:48.880 --> 01:00:50.789
but you have so much of the world in

01:00:50.799 --> 01:00:55.587
you.

01:01:02.079 --> 01:01:06.870
Separate yourself unto me

01:01:10.559 --> 01:01:15.030
and you will see the great

01:01:15.040 --> 01:01:17.829
glory.'There's

01:01:17.839 --> 01:01:19.270
a remnant of you that

01:01:19.280 --> 01:01:23.109
has

01:01:23.119 --> 01:01:25.030
done

01:01:25.040 --> 01:01:26.870
just this;

01:01:26.880 --> 01:01:29.589
you've separated yourself unto me and

01:01:29.599 --> 01:01:37.507
you're ready for the glory.

01:01:37.517 --> 01:01:40.230
But you are few.

01:01:51.680 --> 01:01:59.777
He said

01:02:00.079 --> 01:02:02.789
it reminds him of

01:02:02.799 --> 01:02:04.549
when Moses came down off the

01:02:04.559 --> 01:02:07.270
mountain

01:02:07.280 --> 01:02:08.950
and the children of Israel were acting

01:02:08.950 --> 01:02:08.960
in

01:02:08.960 --> 01:02:16.230
rebellion.

01:02:16.240 --> 01:02:19.030
They built a calf

01:02:19.030 --> 01:02:19.040
and

01:02:19.040 --> 01:02:21.990
did things

01:02:22.000 --> 01:02:34.870
in rebellion unto me.

01:02:34.880 --> 01:02:45.628
But I will use the remnant.

01:02:45.638 --> 01:02:58.230
There

01:03:03.968 --> 01:03:03.978
are

01:03:14.880 --> 01:03:19.190
great days to come.

01:03:19.200 --> 01:03:22.309
He's sending his angel armies

01:03:22.319 --> 01:03:26.230
and there

01:03:26.230 --> 01:03:26.240
will

01:03:26.240 --> 01:03:28.549
be a great revival

01:03:28.559 --> 01:03:30.230
in the

01:03:30.240 --> 01:03:32.789
churches that allow him to flow.

01:03:32.799 --> 01:03:35.349
But there will be a great shaking.

01:03:35.359 --> 01:03:39.190
I see Asia and South Korea again.

01:03:46.480 --> 01:03:49.029
Great persecution.

01:04:29.920 --> 01:04:33.029
He's ready to turn the page

01:04:33.029 --> 01:04:33.039
to

01:04:33.039 --> 01:04:37.349
a new chapter;

01:04:37.359 --> 01:04:39.670
he's out of time.

01:04:39.680 --> 01:04:41.750
He's saying that he's

01:04:41.760 --> 01:04:43.670
going to

01:04:43.680 --> 01:04:45.430
remove

01:04:45.440 --> 01:04:52.950
people who have exalted themselves

01:04:52.960 --> 01:04:56.470
and he will humble them, and he will

01:04:56.480 --> 01:05:00.870
exalt the humble

01:05:00.880 --> 01:05:07.109
ones who have been broken like that.

01:05:11.119 --> 01:05:14.309
It's not a quick

01:05:14.319 --> 01:05:19.349
process;

01:05:19.359 --> 01:05:22.150
it's

01:05:32.010 --> 01:05:35.910
the

01:05:44.799 --> 01:05:48.630
day-to-day.

01:05:50.640 --> 01:05:54.630
So many call him 'Lord,

01:06:03.829 --> 01:06:03.839
Lord,'but

01:06:10.960 --> 01:06:13.670
he doesn't know them.

01:06:13.680 --> 01:06:17.109
You say, 'Lord,

01:06:17.109 --> 01:06:17.119
Lord,'and

01:06:17.119 --> 01:06:20.150
he says,

01:06:20.160 --> 01:06:23.270
'I've done this and

01:06:23.270 --> 01:06:23.280
that,'but

01:06:23.280 --> 01:06:26.069
he

01:06:26.069 --> 01:06:26.079
doesn't

01:06:26.079 --> 01:06:28.470
know

01:06:44.069 --> 01:06:44.079
you.

01:07:05.359 --> 01:07:08.950
It's not about what you do or your works—fasting, praying, helping, giving, or volunteering. It's not about that;

01:07:08.960 --> 01:07:11.190
it's a heart,

01:07:11.200 --> 01:07:17.349
a fragrance, and worship.

01:07:17.359 --> 01:07:20.710
He looks at the heart.

01:07:27.760 --> 01:07:30.069
'For the eyes of the Lord run to and fro

01:07:30.079 --> 01:07:31.670
throughout the whole earth, looking for a

01:07:31.680 --> 01:07:34.470
heart that

01:07:34.470 --> 01:07:34.480
is

01:07:34.480 --> 01:07:37.109
perfect toward

01:07:37.119 --> 01:07:39.589
him.'That's

01:07:39.599 --> 01:07:49.430
what he says.

01:07:49.440 --> 01:07:51.829
Now he's referencing the people in

01:07:51.839 --> 01:07:54.870
Jeremiah.

01:07:54.880 --> 01:07:58.069
He's talking about the prophets

01:07:58.069 --> 01:07:58.079
who

01:07:58.079 --> 01:08:01.109
stood and spoke what the itching

01:08:01.119 --> 01:08:04.549
ears wanted to hear. He

01:08:04.559 --> 01:08:05.990
said, 'There are many of them upon your

01:08:06.000 --> 01:08:08.230
land now.

01:08:08.240 --> 01:08:11.349
I warned you that in the end

01:08:11.359 --> 01:08:13.029
times there

01:08:13.029 --> 01:08:13.039
will

01:08:13.039 --> 01:08:14.870
be many false prophets.

01:08:17.199 --> 01:08:19.189
They are speaking itching-ear words and they

01:08:19.199 --> 01:08:22.070
are

01:08:22.080 --> 01:08:27.669
not of

01:08:27.669 --> 01:08:27.679
me.'That's

01:08:27.679 --> 01:08:30.149
what he just said. 'They're not

01:08:30.159 --> 01:08:33.510
of me, and there are many upon your

01:08:33.510 --> 01:08:33.520
land.'They

01:08:33.520 --> 01:08:35.430
give a good word,

01:08:35.440 --> 01:08:36.470
but

01:08:36.480 --> 01:08:38.229
they sway this way and that

01:08:38.239 --> 01:08:40.390
way. This is

01:08:40.390 --> 01:08:40.400
what

01:08:40.400 --> 01:08:42.789
I see in

01:08:42.799 --> 01:08:44.550
the spirit

01:08:44.550 --> 01:08:44.560
realm—it's

01:08:44.560 --> 01:08:46.390
like twigs.

01:08:46.400 --> 01:08:49.030
You sway

01:08:49.040 --> 01:08:51.030
with what he says one day and you sway

01:08:51.040 --> 01:08:52.870
over here because you want to

01:08:52.880 --> 01:08:54.309
draw close to the people because it's

01:08:54.319 --> 01:08:57.189
about finances to

01:08:57.189 --> 01:08:57.199
them—money,

01:08:57.199 --> 01:08:59.910
money, money. But

01:08:59.910 --> 01:08:59.920
you've

01:08:59.920 --> 01:09:01.990
got to have a word from the Lord. They

01:09:01.990 --> 01:09:02.000
try to

01:09:02.000 --> 01:09:05.590
speak for

01:09:05.590 --> 01:09:05.600
him

01:09:05.600 --> 01:09:08.789
and they sway

01:09:13.040 --> 01:09:14.789
to the people to get the

01:09:14.799 --> 01:09:17.030
money.

01:09:17.040 --> 01:09:23.430
Jeremiah—that's

01:09:23.440 --> 01:09:25.110
what he's talking

01:09:25.120 --> 01:09:28.070
about. You're people

01:09:28.080 --> 01:09:30.630
pleasers.

01:09:30.640 --> 01:09:32.630
He said

01:09:32.640 --> 01:09:34.709
they've been castrated by the

01:09:34.719 --> 01:09:43.110
world.

01:09:43.120 --> 01:09:45.349
Many false prophets will rise in the

01:09:45.359 --> 01:09:48.149
day and you're seeing it all

01:09:48.159 --> 01:09:51.030
around you. Church, wake up!

01:09:51.040 --> 01:09:52.950
Have greater

01:09:52.960 --> 01:09:56.229
discernment in whom you're

01:09:58.640 --> 01:10:03.110
listening to.

01:10:03.120 --> 01:10:04.950
That's what the Lord just said.

01:10:18.640 --> 01:10:21.510
Stay humble before me

01:10:21.520 --> 01:10:27.110
like David,

01:10:27.120 --> 01:10:30.070
for I look at the heart, not at the

01:10:30.080 --> 01:10:34.390
outward. I look at the heart, not the

01:10:34.400 --> 01:10:38.870
tall like

01:10:38.870 --> 01:10:38.880
Saul—head

01:10:38.880 --> 01:10:41.189
and shoulders above

01:10:41.189 --> 01:10:41.199
the rest.

01:10:41.199 --> 01:10:43.510
The world looks at

01:10:43.520 --> 01:10:51.189
the outward; I look at the inward

01:10:51.199 --> 01:10:53.189
and I'll take the foolish things of the

01:10:53.199 --> 01:10:55.750
world to confound the wise.

01:10:55.760 --> 01:11:00.310
Don't be moved by their size

01:11:00.310 --> 01:11:00.320
or

01:11:00.320 --> 01:11:03.270
what they look like on

01:11:03.280 --> 01:11:06.390
the outside. Flow with the Holy Ghost

01:11:06.390 --> 01:11:06.400
and

01:11:06.400 --> 01:11:09.110
my presence. There

01:11:09.110 --> 01:11:09.120
are

01:11:09.120 --> 01:11:12.149
great people whom you do not know

01:11:14.470 --> 01:11:14.480
who

01:11:16.320 --> 01:11:18.870
are about to come up to the

01:11:18.880 --> 01:11:20.390
forefront. They may not be the

01:11:20.400 --> 01:11:22.390
prettiest or the

01:11:22.390 --> 01:11:22.400
richest, but

01:11:22.400 --> 01:11:25.350
they

01:11:25.360 --> 01:11:26.950
have

01:11:26.960 --> 01:11:28.790
poise; they

01:11:28.790 --> 01:11:28.800
are

01:11:28.800 --> 01:11:30.870
people who are like the broken

01:11:30.880 --> 01:11:33.510
horse.

01:11:33.520 --> 01:11:37.590
And he said, 'I can use that,

01:11:37.600 --> 01:11:41.990
Brandon.

01:11:42.000 --> 01:11:44.229
It's the

01:11:44.229 --> 01:11:44.239
horse—the

01:11:44.239 --> 01:11:47.110
warhorse. Pressure—you're

01:11:47.110 --> 01:11:47.120
built for

01:11:47.120 --> 01:11:49.990
pressure. You're

01:11:49.990 --> 01:11:50.000
the

01:11:50.000 --> 01:11:52.550
closers.'I

01:11:52.560 --> 01:11:54.149
feel the Holy Ghost and fire all over

01:11:54.159 --> 01:11:59.990
me.

01:12:00.000 --> 01:12:02.310
And you will walk with great signs and

01:12:02.320 --> 01:12:04.149
wonders;

01:12:08.080 --> 01:12:13.110
they will know you by your fruit.

01:12:13.120 --> 01:12:15.430
True prophetic, true ministers of

01:12:15.430 --> 01:12:15.440
me—they'll

01:12:15.440 --> 01:12:17.430
know you by your fruit. There

01:12:17.430 --> 01:12:17.440
will

01:12:17.440 --> 01:12:22.229
be a great line; he drew a line

01:12:22.239 --> 01:12:24.709
in the sand. 'Who

01:12:24.719 --> 01:12:27.430
is on my side?

01:12:27.440 --> 01:12:30.390
Who is on the Lord's side?

01:12:30.400 --> 01:12:34.870
Who is really truly with me?'he says.

01:12:34.880 --> 01:12:38.390
'For I have

01:12:38.400 --> 01:12:43.830
drawn the line.

01:12:43.840 --> 01:12:48.630
There's

01:12:48.640 --> 01:12:54.149
no more playing church,

01:12:54.159 --> 01:12:57.990
for the cup is full before me

01:12:58.000 --> 01:13:11.830
and time is short.

01:13:11.840 --> 01:13:16.550
The Hollywood celebrity is over.

01:13:16.560 --> 01:13:19.030
I will not share my glory with any of

01:13:19.040 --> 01:13:21.510
them.

